title: 1971 Das Aggressive Braune Wasser in den Leitungent des Professors (the aggressive brown water in the tubes of the Professor)

sources.title: 1971 Das Aggressive Braune Wasser in den Leitungent des Professors (the aggressive brown water in the tubes of the Professor)
sources.description: Featuring Jurgen Kuhfuss Meiterinnen and Andreas Dahmen vom Mieterverein. An attempt by the film maker himself to make himself useful in the tenant solidarity movement against mass dismissals.
